net.proteusframework.core.mail

Class MemoryMailPart

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.core.mail.AbstractMailPart
      • net.proteusframework.core.mail.MemoryMailPart
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSource, MailPart

    public class MemoryMailPart
extends AbstractMailPart
implements MailPart, DataSource
    MailPart backed stored in memory. Note: MailMessage.release() calls MailPart.close() on all the parts in the message.
    Author:
    Russell Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
